cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with object tracking using deep learning techniques, specifically for thermal infrared (TIR) images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a Siamese network and an ensemble subnetwork, which are common techniques in machine learning and deep learning, respectively, indicating that the paper could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the use of a dataset, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
